    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Testicular tenderness, edema\nMay see erythema of overlying scrotum\nViral orchitis\nAbrupt onset of scrotal pain/swelling 4-7 days after onset of parotitis\n[1]\nUsually unilateral\nFever\n,\ntachycardia\nInguinal\nlymphadenopathy\nPatient uncomfortable while seated",
