    "Management": {
      "text": "Viral orchitis (mumps): supportive care, cold packs, scrotal elevation,\nanalgesia\n.\nBacterial orchitis (epididymo-orchitis):\n<35yo (assume sexually transmitted):\nCeftriaxone\n250mg IM x1\nAND\nDoxycycline\n100mg PO BID x14 days\nOR\nAzithromycin\n1gm x1\nAlso treat sexual partner\n>35yo, NO history of anal intercourse and NOT sexually active:\nOfloxacin 300mg PO BID x14 days\nOR\nlevofloxacin\n500mg QD x10 days\nOR\nciprofloxacin\n500mg PO BID x14 days\nIV:\npiperacillin/tazobactam\n3.375g IV q6 or\nampicillin/sulbactam\n3g IV q6",
      "subsections": {},
